For the 2nd day in a row, #Wales has reported record #vaccine numbers.
33, 955 1st Doses and 836 2nd Doses were reported today. 
The total vaccine levels are increasing at a steeper rate, notably in 2nd Doses. 556,997 have now had a first dose (17% of Wales). 
#Covid19UK #Covid19 https://t.co/17a78Trmo2
